{"tid":606591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[HK NoIT]03-26「四仔」售200元10隻　警破旺角色情光碟中心","createTime":"2018-03-26T15:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T15:27:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"07f4317ebfdcb44fc594916e7a2352910688f8ab","tid":606591,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T15:01:26.000Z","msg":"旺角警區特別職務隊根據線報及深入調查，在旺角多處地方掃蕩色情光碟店，並在行動中突擊搜查旺角通菜街14號、砵蘭街181號及亞皆老街83號3個單位，搗破共3個色情光碟銷售中心，拘捕3人，包括50歲姓何男子、63歲姓鄭男子及70歲姓陳男子。被捕人涉嫌「管有淫褻物品以供發布用途」被捕，現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方共檢獲約1,5000隻色情光碟、一批色情海報及約1,000元現金。該批光碟總值約3萬元。旺角警區特別職務隊第二隊主管張天朗督察表示，銷售中心由黑幫操控，已經營約半年，警方相信行動已切斷黑幫其中一個收入來源。據了解，中心的顧客以熟客為主，平日僅低調宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1308303/org/173f1665bc75e8923d288313f740bf50.jpg/6kU-8aWSLFvoukdBAEitZeUBgDVG5QwFLforgy36K4M?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1308303%2Forg%2F173f1665bc75e8923d288313f740bf50.jpg%2F6kU-8aWSLFvoukdBAEitZeUBgDVG5QwFLforgy36K4M%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=8ea8587c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/172060/%E5%9B%9B%E4%BB%94-%E5%94%AE200%E5%85%8310%E9%9A%BB-%E8%AD%A6%E7%A0%B4%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E5%85%89%E7%A2%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E6%AA%A2%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%94%E9%9A%BB%E5%85%89%E7%A2%9F%E6%8B%983%E7%94%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F172060%2F%25E5%259B%259B%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E5%2594%25AE200%25E5%2585%258310%25E9%259A%25BB-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%2589%25B2%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%25A2%259F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%2594%25E9%259A%25BB%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%25A2%259F%25E6%258B%25983%25E7%2594%25B7&d=77LTAM%2BkkH8ks%2FmAMaxNoIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=4b24a1b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/172060/%E5%9B%9B%E4%BB%94-%E5%94%AE20